    <item>
      <title>波兰和摩尔多瓦寻求帮助乌克兰加强电力安全</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-08/poland-and-moldova-seek-to-help-ukraine-boost-power-security</link>
      <description><![CDATA[近期俄罗斯多次袭击乌克兰电力设施，波兰和摩尔多瓦正在寻找方法帮助乌克兰加强电力安全。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-08/poland-and-moldova-seek-to-help-ukraine-boost-power-security</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 08 Jul 2024 17:05:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国将扩大对军事基地附近外国投资的审查</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-08/us-to-expand-scrutiny-of-foreign-investments-near-military-bases</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国财政部将扩大对军事基地附近外国投资的审查，以应对来自中国和其他国家的可疑安全威胁。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-08/us-to-expand-scrutiny-of-foreign-investments-near-military-bases</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 08 Jul 2024 17:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>北约支持在发生海底袭击时通过重新路由到太空来拯救互联网的努力</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-08/nato-backs-effort-to-reroute-internet-to-space-in-event-of-subsea-attacks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[北约正在帮助资助一个项目，该项目旨在寻找在欧洲海域传输民用和军事通信的海底电缆受到攻击时维持互联网运行的方法。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-08/nato-backs-effort-to-reroute-internet-to-space-in-event-of-subsea-attacks</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 08 Jul 2024 16:38:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>喀麦隆总统比亚将延长议员任期，投票推翻反对派</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-08/cameroon-s-biya-to-extend-mp-mandates-quash-opposition-in-vote</link>
      <description><![CDATA[喀麦隆议会开始审议一项法案，旨在将议员的任期延长一年，此举可能从技术上消除 2025 年总统选举中的任何反对派。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-08/cameroon-s-biya-to-extend-mp-mandates-quash-opposition-in-vote</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 08 Jul 2024 16:36:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
