      <title>奥尔班的穿梭外交激怒欧洲并打击盟友</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-08/orban-meeting-xi-and-putin-puts-him-at-odds-with-eu-over-ukraine</link>
